The paper deals with a problem in computational geometry, specifically the curve simplification problem. Therefore, cs.CG (Computational Geometry) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves algorithms and complexity analysis, which suggests that it could belong to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.CC (Computational Complexity). The use of distance measures and optimization techniques suggests that it could also belong to cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
